# Testing

## Local (Developer Skills)

| Flow | Command | Pass when |
|------|---------|-----------|
| Story workflow | `/dx-req <ID>` then `/dx-plan` then `/dx-agent-all` | Spec files created, steps executed, PR created |
| Bug fix | `/dx-bug-all <ID>` | Triage + fix, no `[ALERT:CRITICAL]` |
| PR review | `/dx-pr-review <PR>` then `/dx-pr-answer` | Review posted, answers drafted |
| AEM verify | `/aem-snapshot <comp>` then `/aem-verify <comp>` | Before/after snapshots captured |
| Dry run | `/auto-test dor <ID> --dryRun` | Agent runs, nothing posted to ADO |
| Eval gates | `/auto-eval --all` | All fixtures pass |
| Unit tests | `node --test .ai/automation/agents/lib/__tests__/*.test.mjs` | All green |
| Health check | `/dx-doctor` and `/auto-doctor` | All checks pass |

## Remote (Autonomous Agents)

| Step | Action | Pass when |
|------|--------|-----------|
| Health | `/auto-doctor` + `/auto-status` | All green, DLQ = 0 |
| DoR trigger | Add `KAI-DOR-AUTOMATION` + `KAI-TRIGGER` tags | Comment within 1-2 min |
| PR Review | Create PR targeting base branch | Review comments posted |
| PR Answer | Post comment on your PR | Reply in thread |
| Dedupe | Re-apply same tag | Lambda returns `status: skipped` |
| Monitoring | Check CloudWatch alarms | 4 alarms in `OK` state |

